md:
giải nghĩa từ "decorations" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.
Decorations /dɪˈkɔːrɪʃənz/ (noun)
- Plural form of decoration

Meaning:

* Trang trí, đồ trang trí (noun)

Example sentence:
The hotel lobby was filled with beautiful decorations, including a large Christmas tree and sparkling lights.

Related words:
- Decoration (noun)
- Decorate (verb)
- Decorative (adjective)

Note: Decorations can refer to the act of decorating or the things used to decorate something, such as ornaments, lights, or other embellishments.
